79
00:04:32,004 --> 00:04:35,334
The way it opens is so distinctive, huh?

80
00:04:35,534 --> 00:04:37,834
Yeah! It really looks like it!

81
00:04:39,074 --> 00:04:42,804
Um, I said I like this?

82
00:04:43,174 --> 00:04:44,844
What could it be?

83
00:04:44,844 --> 00:04:46,714
I wonder if it looks like it...

84
00:04:46,714 --> 00:04:48,184
Yeah.

85
00:04:49,684 --> 00:04:51,314
A Halloween party?

86
00:04:51,654 --> 00:04:53,244
Why all of a sudden?

87
00:04:53,384 --> 00:04:56,594
Some things happened this morning,
and we started talking about it.

88
00:04:56,594 --> 00:04:59,224
I've been interested in Halloween for a while.

89
00:04:59,224 --> 00:05:02,994
Tomorrow's Saturday,
so let's all make some sweets and eat them!

90
00:05:02,994 --> 00:05:04,934
I look forward to it!

91
