Cookies or something? Or cakes?

92
00:05:10,174 --> 00:05:11,704
I'll pass.

93
00:05:11,704 --> 00:05:12,844
Huh?

94
00:05:12,844 --> 00:05:15,474
Nagi, you don't like making sweets?

95
00:05:15,474 --> 00:05:20,784
