That's not for me.

96
00:05:20,784 --> 00:05:23,374
Also, I'm on a diet.

97
00:05:23,924 --> 00:05:25,654
Don't worry about it.

98
00:05:25,654 --> 00:05:29,284
I'll measure out the calories for you, Nagi.

99
00:05:29,954 --> 00:05:31,164
Really?

100
00:05:31,164 --> 00:05:32,324
Yeah.

101
00:05:32,624 --> 00:05:34,434
Well, if I only have to eat...

102
00:05:34,434 --> 00:05:35,194
Okay!

103
00:05:35,634 --> 00:05:37,154
What about you, Toru?

104
00:05:38,634 --> 00:05:40,734
I think I'll be a little late.

105
00:05:40,734 --> 00:05:42,104
Oh.

106
00:05:42,104 --> 00:05:44,804
I'll come over and eat some once they're done.

107
00:05:44,804 --> 00:05:46,104
Sure, okay!

108
00:05:46,104 --> 00:05:49,604
Oh, then I'll show up later with Toru.

109
00:05:49,944 --> 00:05:50,914
Okay.

110
00:05:51,144 --> 00:05:54,484
Well, Yuko-chan, want to make them with me?

111
00:05:54,484 --> 00:05:57,944
Sure. Is there anything I should bring over?

112
00:05:58,884 --> 00:06:03,294
My mom makes sweets,
so I think we have just about everything.

113
00:06:03,294 --> 00:06:05,764
Oh. I'm lookin' forward to it!

114
00:06:05,924 --> 00:06:08,264
Okay, let's do it tomorrow!

115
00:06:08,364 --> 00:06:09,524
Yeah!

116
00:06:24,344 --> 00:06:26,334
Run, what are you drawing?

117
00:06:28,314 --> 00:06:33,224
Look. Toru and I are exchanging diaries.
We're doing a drawing game!

118
00:06:37,094 --> 00:06:38,784
What does it look like?

119
00:06:39,494 --> 00:06:42,294
It's the "stuffed animal incident" again!

120
00:06:50,404 --> 00:06:54,774
Is that even an animal?
It looks kinda like a bug...

121
00:06:55,174 --> 00:06:57,544
Maybe it's a little difficult to tell.

122
00:06:58,444 --> 00:07:02,214
Okay, here's a hint: it's often eaten.

123
00:07:04,184 --> 00:07:05,674
People eat it?!

124
00:07:05,824 --> 00:07:07,814
That was a big one.

125
00:07:08,254 --> 00:07:10,084
It's a zebra, isn't it?

126
00:07:10,694 --> 00:07:12,224
Toru, that's right!

127
00:07:12,224 --> 00:07:12,884
