131
00:07:23,944 --> 00:07:25,774
Nagi, you're over-thinking it.

132
00:07:31,944 --> 00:07:35,884
I don't mind taking it, but this thing is a bit scary.

133
00:07:35,984 --> 00:07:38,184
You're not going home yet?

134
00:07:38,424 --> 00:07:40,354
No, I'm going.

135
00:07:41,024 --> 00:07:45,164
Come to think of it, do you want to meet before
going to Run-chan's house tomorrow?

136
00:07:45,164 --> 00:07:47,394
Yeah, that would help me out.

137
00:07:47,794 --> 00:07:51,804
So, the station's north exit,
near the entrance to the shopping arcade.

138
00:07:51,804 --> 00:07:52,854
Okay.

139
00:07:55,874 --> 00:07:58,204
Toru! Th-that!

140
00:07:59,974 --> 00:08:02,744
This? I got it from Run-chan.

141
00:08:02,974 --> 00:08:04,884
