145
00:08:20,564 --> 00:08:23,324
Why? This is really irritating!

146
00:08:24,504 --> 00:08:27,364
The truth is, I got the same kind of thing.

147
00:08:28,074 --> 00:08:29,464
It's so big!

148
00:08:33,374 --> 00:08:34,634
