149
00:08:38,114 --> 00:08:40,014
Please, you MUST give me that!

150
00:08:40,014 --> 00:08:43,674
Huh? No way. This is mine.

151
00:08:43,924 --> 00:08:45,454
Don't say that!

152
00:08:45,454 --> 00:08:46,554
No, no.

153
00:08:46,554 --> 00:08:48,054
