It's not cruel at all.

155
00:08:50,024 --> 00:08:51,424
Sorry for the wait.

156
00:08:52,064 --> 00:08:53,684
Well, shall we go?

157
00:08:54,064 --> 00:08:56,194
I'll get things ready, so wait for me, okay?

158
00:08:56,294 --> 00:08:58,564
Yeah. But hurry.

159
00:09:01,434 --> 00:09:02,924
