169
00:09:31,564 --> 00:09:32,764
You wanna know?
I'm all ready!

170
00:09:32,764 --> 00:09:33,164
Yes, I do! Come on, come on, come on!
I'm all ready!

171
00:09:33,164 --> 00:09:34,364
Yes, I do! Come on, come on, come on!

172
00:09:34,574 --> 00:09:36,434
Please, tell me!

173
00:09:36,434 --> 00:09:38,044
They're cute, aren't they? Squirrels.

174
00:09:38,044 --> 00:09:39,874
Come on, Toru!

175
00:09:39,874 --> 00:09:40,444
Small animals.

176
00:09:40,444 --> 00:09:41,274
What do you think they're talking about?

177
00:09:41,274 --> 00:09:42,444
Tell me!
What do you think they're talking about?

178
00:09:42,444 --> 00:09:44,034
Tell me!
Beats me.

179
00:09:45,744 --> 00:09:47,074
I'm home.

180
